comment._content: Centaur T (Serial No. TC-9) used in the failed attempt to launch ELINT/SIGINT satellite Mercury 3 on August 12, 1998. space.skyrocket.de/doc_sdat/mercury.htm Centaur T (Serial No. TC-10) used to launch Trumpet 1 (USA 103) SIGINT satellite on May 3, 1994. space.skyrocket.de/doc_sdat/trumpet.htm
